item.title: CVE-2017-8174|2024-09-17T01:56:13.061Z -- huawei%20technologies%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- secospace%20usg6300%2Csecospace%20usg6600
item.description: Huawei USG6300 V100R001C30SPC300 and USG6600 with software of V100R001C30SPC500,V100R001C30SPC600,V100R001C30SPC700,V100R001C30SPC800 have a weak algorithm vulnerability. Attackers may exploit the weak algorithm vulnerability to crack the cipher text and cause confidential information leaks on the transmission links.
